				\begin{document}$${\text{AUC}} = \mathop \int \limits_{0}^{24} C(t){\text{d}}t,$$\end{document}AUC=∫024C(t)dt,where C is cycloserine concentration.

Cycloserine half-life was calculated according to Eq. (3):3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
