The strength of unconjugated bilirubin binding to albumin was calculated according to Eq. (5) [24]:5\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
